https://world.openfoodfacts.org/
https://pl.openfoodfacts.org/

Search for Products (e.g., Milk in Poland)
GET https://pl.openfoodfacts.org/cgi/search.pl?search_terms=milk&search_simple=1&action=process&json=1

Get Product by Barcode
GET https://world.openfoodfacts.org/api/v0/product/5901234123457.json

When using search.pl, here are some useful query parameters:

search_terms=milk
search_simple=1
action=process
json=1 (to get JSON response)
fields=product_name,nutrition_grades_tags,countries_tags
page_size=20 (limit number of results)

https://world.openfoodfacts.org/cgi/search.pl?search_terms=bread&json=1&fields=product_name,countries_tags&country=pl

